title: Enemy Territory: Quake Wars [PC] - TheHerb
description:
06/07/2008
Enemy Territory: Quake Wars ISO (No CD Key needed)

Minimum System Requirements

*Microsoft Windows XP/Vista
*128 MB NVIDIA Geforce 5700 or ATI Radeon 9700
**Intel Pentium 4 2.8 Ghz or AMD Athlon XP 2800+ processor
*512MB RAM
*5 GB of free hard drive space, plus 700MB for Windows swap file
*Microsoft DirectX 9.0c (included)
*100% DirectX 9.0c compatible sound card
*Broadband connection and service required for full gameplay and downloads
*Mouse and keyboard
*4X DVD-ROM drive (600 K/sec sustained transfer rate)
*Supported Video Chipsets: NVIDIA GeforceFX Series (5700 or higher, not including 5700LE and 5700VE), NVIDIA Geforce 6 Series (6200 or higher) NVIDIA Geforce 7 Series (7300 or higher), NVIDIA Geforce 8 Series, ATI Radeon 9700 or higher, ATI Radeon X700 or higher, ATI Radeon X1650 or higher.

Gamespot Score

8.5 - Great

Gamespot Summary

Quake Wars&#039; strong shooting model and focused objectives make it a lot of fun to play.
